org.spongepowered.api.data

Interface LocatableSnapshot<T extends LocatableSnapshot<T>>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of location snapshot for self referencing
    All Superinterfaces:
    DataSerializable, ImmutableDataHolder<T>, ImmutableValueStore<T,ImmutableDataManipulator<?,?>>, PropertyHolder, ValueContainer<T>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    BlockSnapshot, EntitySnapshot

    public interface LocatableSnapshot<T extends LocatableSnapshot<T>>
extends ImmutableDataHolder<T>
    A type of ImmutableDataHolder that may be linked to a particular Location. Being that a LocatableSnapshot may be built by an ImmutableDataBuilder, the Location may be null such that getLocation() returns Optional.empty().
